window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Secret of the Old Ones is a deep dive VR game the likes of which the world had never seen. </p> <p>Trent Noguero, a hardcore gamer, has been playing for a year and is about to get his big break. He is about to catapult himself into the ranks of the most powerful players in the world. </p> <p>However, power comes with a price, and celebrity creates enemies. Trent has the keys to massive success, but he also accidentally painted a target on his back...both in, and out of the game. </p>"; 
